wait 0
show "3black.png" 0.5:0.5 0.5:0.5 2000:960 fade(0,linear) normal
wait 2
play "sand_epilogue.ogg" 1.0

say "\"It's raining...\""

play "rain.ogg" 0 loop
volume "rain.ogg" 0.1 3.0
show "nihil/nihil_1_cut1.jpg" 0.5:0 0.5:0 2:2 fade(5,linear) normal
move "nihil/nihil_1_cut1.jpg" 0:-900 21 sineout

say "Vita came to me in a corner of my glass library, and told me that.
In the bright and dark cave, I looked up to her from where I sat, and then I looked away.
Rain..."

say "In all my years in this place, I had never seen rain, and now rain and snow
and thunder and lightning all had been seen by us on the horizons every so often.
And now it was there."

say "I stood.
\"Vita...\" I began,
\"we will be going, and when you follow: you will follow and hide behind.\""

say "\"'Going'...? Where?\""

say "\"To Lethe,\" I said, \"to kill her.\""

play "1step.ogg" 0.5
hide "nihil/nihil_1_cut1.jpg" fade(0.1,linear)

say "I walked past her and, after descending,
made my way to the mountain's lowest exit.
Vita was delayed, but followed just as instructed."

say "\"...'Kill'—what!? No!\""

play "lastBreak.ogg" 1.0
volume "rain.ogg" 0.7 9.0

say "She shouted at my back, followed me all the way down,
and trotted out behind me as I went into the rain."

say "She protested, protested."

play "collapse.ogg" 0.5

say "She grabbed my cape and I pulled it from her hands."

play "cut.ogg" 0.3

say "She picked up a stone, and threw it at my back.
I kept on, and finally she screamed:"

say "\"Why!?\""

volume "rain.ogg" 1.0 3.0
show "nihil/nihil_1_cut2.jpg" 0.5:1 0.5:1 1.2:1.2 fade(6,linear) normal
move "nihil/nihil_1_cut2.jpg" -15:0 5 linear

say "Rain fell on and between us as I stopped and turned to face her.
She met my eye. Her red and white eyes were shimmering."

say "\"Vita...\" I said, \"this world is dying.\""

show "nihil/nihil_1A.jpg" 0.4:0.4 0.4:0.4 0.83:0.83 fade(4,linear) normal
move "nihil/nihil_1A.jpg" -20:0 7 linear
move "nihil/nihil_1B.jpg" -20:0 7 linear

say "\"Yes...\" she muttered and at the time I thought—Ah, so she knows.
\"So... So why would you want to... kill...?\""

say "\"I felt something in what she gathered, something I have never felt in what we have built,\" I explained."

say "\"If... I want to rescue us all, I reason that I must discover what that something was,
and take and use it. With it, I might make the miracle that will build a new world.
Lethe, however, won't understand the theory, and we have no time to try with her.\""

say "\"Her belief... How she lies to herself would never let her reason. Her heart is a fire.
She will aim those feelings at me, and we will come to blows.\""

hide "nihil/nihil_1_cut2.jpg" fade(0,linear)
hide "3black.png" fade(0,linear)
wait 0
hide "nihil/nihil_1A.jpg" fade(0.3,linear)

say "\"You won't try?\" she accused me, and I smiled.
\"You should at least try!\" Her face bunched up, and her fists balled."

stop "rain.ogg" 6.0

say "And, when I turned from her again—
as the rains around us slowed, and then stopped—
I said, lightly: \"Fair. Watch safely away when I do.\""

play "breath.ogg" 1.0
play "wind.ogg" 0.0 loop
volume "wind.ogg" 0.3 6.0
hide "nihil/nihil_1B.jpg" fade(6,linear)

move "nihil/bg_cut1.jpg" -426:0 19 sineout
move "nihil/bg_cut2.jpg" 426:0 19 sineout
move "nihil/bg_cut3.jpg" -426:0 19 sineout
move "nihil/bg_cut3.jpg" 0:1300 30 sineout

say "I have taken much of my own glass to Lethe's place.
As I approach there, our collections almost meet,
but never blend together."

say "It is bright. On this cliff's edge, the world is bright from glass.
Lethe, beneath it, is cloaked in shadows.
Over the edge, the Void yawns."

say "\"Reaper,\" I call to her, \"let's put pettiness aside. Help me.\""

say "\"Help you?\" she spits. \"After you've done all this!?\""

say "Ah.
She must think I'm responsible for cracking this world at its core.
...She thinks so little of me."

say "I glance behind myself and, unable to see Vita, I turn back to Lethe
and continue our conversation."

stop "wind.ogg" 0.3
hide "nihil/bg_cut1.jpg" fade(0.1,linear)
hide "nihil/bg_cut2.jpg" fade(0.1,linear)
hide "nihil/bg_cut3.jpg" fade(0.1,linear)
hide "black.png" fade(0.1,linear)
hide "2black.png" fade(0.1,linear)

say "It goes, and ends, as terribly as one can imagine."

