show "finale/vs_overlay.png" 0.21:0.75 0.21:0.75 1.3:1.3 fade(0.1,sinein) normal

play "slip.ogg" 1.0
say "I travel from shard to shard with a little trick of the flower at my eye.
I refrain. I turn around her. I try. I am trying.
Until I no longer can."

play "ruffle.ogg" 1.0

show "2white.png" 0.5:0.5 0.5:0.5 2000:960 fade(0.1,linear) normal
